OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FGolden eagles could return to England,
OL,7,Fthe government has said, as it
OL,8,Fannounced new funding to explore their
OL,9,Freintroduction.
OL,11,FThe species was once widespread across
OL,12,FEngland, but it was virtually wiped
OL,13,Fout by sheep farmers and gamekeepers
OL,14,Fin the Victorian era, who viewed them
OL,15,Fas a threat to lambs and game birds,
OL,16,Fcompounded by 20th-century pesticide
OL,17,Fuse affecting their fertility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
