OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776070596
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FOnly a handful of pairs have been seen
OL,7,Fin England in the last 150 years, with
OL,8,Fthe last eagle dying in the Lake
OL,9,FDistrict in 2016, though they are
OL,10,Fstill found in Scotland.
OL,12,FA study by Forestry England, published
OL,13,Fon Sunday, found that England now has
OL,14,Fthe capacity to sustain golden eagle
OL,15,Fpopulations again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
