CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776070596
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FThe paper identified eight potential
OL,7,F"recovery zones" as the most suitable
OL,8,Fareas, mostly in the north of England,
OL,9,Falthough it could take more than a
OL,10,Fdecade until breeding populations are
OL,11,Festablished in the area.
OL,13,FIn response, Environment Secretary
OL,14,FEmma Reynolds approved #1 million in
OL,15,Fadditional funding to help pave the
OL,16,Fway for a recovery programme. This
OL,17,Fcould include reintroduction efforts
OL,18,Fthat would see juveniles aged six to
OL,19,Feight weeks old released as early as
OL,20,Fnext year.
