OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FReynolds said: "This government is
OL,7,Fcommitted to protecting and restoring
OL,8,Four most threatened native wildlife `
OL,9,Fand that includes bringing back iconic
OL,10,Fspecies like the golden eagle.
OL,12,F"Backed by #1 million of government
OL,13,Ffunding ` we will work alongside
OL,14,Fpartners and communities to make the
OL,15,Fgolden eagle a feature of English
OL,16,Flandscapes once again."
OL,18,FIn Southern Scotland, golden eagle
OL,19,Fpopulations have recovered to record
OL,20,Fnumbers because of a major project to
OL,21,Frestore their populations in the area.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOUxD@WO]
