OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776070596
OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FSatellite tracking indicates that some
OL,7,Fof these translocated birds have
OL,8,Falready begun to fly across the border
OL,9,Fand explore northern England, the
OL,10,Fgovernment said.
OL,12,FIt is hoped the new funding will help
OL,13,Fto support these birds in England,
OL,14,Fcoupled with targeted reintroductions.
OL,16,FForestry England's research found that
OL,17,FScottish birds could be seen across
OL,18,Fnorthern England within 10 years, but
OL,19,Fit will take longer for breeding
OL,20,Fgolden eagles to become established in
OL,21,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
