OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMike Seddon, Forestry England chief
OL,12,Fexecutive, said: "The detailed
OL,13,Ffindings of our feasibility study will
OL,14,Fguide us with our partners, Restoring
OL,15,FUpland Nature, to take the next steps
OL,16,Fto explore the recovery of golden
OL,17,Feagles in northern England.
