OL,3,CGolden eagles could be reintroduced to
OL,4,CEngland with new funding, ministers say
OL,6,FThe funding comes as part of the #60
OL,7,Fmillion in species recovery funding
OL,8,Fannounced by the Environment
OL,9,FDepartment last week. It ties into
OL,10,Fwork aimed at meeting the UK's legally
OL,11,Fbinding target to halt the decline in
OL,12,Fspecies abundance by 2030 and reduce
OL,13,Fspecies extinction risk by 2042
OL,14,Fagainst 2022 levels.
